title: West Virginia donors who gave to campaigns of one of these Republican presidential candidates: Huckabee, Romney, Giuliani, McCain, Thompson, Ron Paul, Tancredo, Hunter
name: West Virginia donors who gave to campaigns of one of these Republican presidential candidates: Huckabee, Romney, Giuliani, McCain, Thompson, Ron Paul, Tancredo, Hunter
description: The map is based on three quarterly campaign finance reports submitted by the leading Republican presidential candidates to Federal Election Commission                              So far West Virgina individual donations to GOP presidential candidates came to nearly $180,000.  For last several elections, West Virginia has been voting for Republican presidents and democratic for state and senate elections.                         This data is available at: http://www.fec.govand was accessed on December 11, 2007.                              FEC Notice: Reports and statements filed by political committees may be inspected and copied by anyone. The names and addresses of individual contributors, however, may not be sold or used for any commercial purpose or to solicit any type of contribution or donation, such as political or charitable contributions. 2 U.S.C.
